info.name: WeSeeDoPersonal-WeSeeDo
info.description:
The WeSeeDo Personal API allows video calling in the right way and distinguishes itself in human contact, ease of use and safety. ### Key highlights - **Sandbox:** Full-fledged capabilities. - **Security:** HTTPS, OAuth, Rate limit. - **Versioning:** Supports version-less API, version tight. If no version is provided (in header) it defaults to latest version. --- [KPN Developer](https://developer.kpn.com/)
[Getting Started](https://developer.kpn.com/getting-started) --- Contact Support: Name: API Support Email: api_developer@kpn.com
